1-01-31T21:26:53.000Z","msg":"大陸金融工具未用盡，仲有好多空間減息同調低銀行準備金黎刺激經濟，有排玩。<br />\n相反歐美已經用盡方法，剩返量化寬鬆，即印銀紙黎舒緩經濟危機。。。"},{"pid":"5ccbef8d134c344db61ea9cb3925f9854bd98123","tid":2389192,"uid":237459,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T23:27:23.000Z","msg":"美國已經輸咗了"},{"pid":"5a2464347dbb394234173294fd06fa4fdc60fff0","tid":2389192,"uid":217555,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T23:28:55.000Z","msg":"唔係2010已經超左咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f62046e1f6237b60423d2d9d22f32cb013c3dd0","tid":2389192,"uid":34666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5ccbef8d134c344db61ea9cb3925f9854bd98123","tid":2389192,"uid":237459,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T23:27:23.000Z","msg":"美國已經輸咗了"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T23:31:02.000Z","msg":"你地臭閪蚑那通化贏咗了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08675527f345134fac2f783c71be4ca318c9113a","tid":2389192,"uid":342990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5a2464347dbb394234173294fd06fa4fdc60fff0","tid":2389192,"uid":217555,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T23:28:55.000Z","msg":"唔係2010已經超左咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T23:37:59.000Z","msg":"個個係超越日本？"},{"pid":"b6bbe9aac83c1df4a997eb979185cf6dc3aa8211","tid":2389192,"uid":93588,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T23:46:46.000Z","msg":"即係用肺炎做生代武器打殘美國啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n毫無道德仲咁口響真係得中国人先做到"},{"pid":"a709ccfcd345c71e2349af1cb1b42c6b3d5a2031","tid":2389192,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T16:39:05.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"0b1140b315401cfa9ce2d632e7f1583fe796c288","tid":2389192,"uid":321002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T17:53:03.000Z","msg":"講錯左，國㥽啊<i